welcome_message_body: Welcome to Santee, a charming city known for its beautiful lakes, outdoor recreation, and friendly community. We hope you enjoy your time here and take the opportunity to explore all that Santee has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gillespie Field Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network while waiting for their flight.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal for domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The secondary terminal for domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at North Island NAS Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at North Island NAS Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 2 hours.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Brown Field Municipal Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Brown Field Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal of Mc Clellan-Palomar Airport, serving all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: A separate terminal for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
